Swing to determine the<hex:02100103>number of mining attempts.<hex:02100103>The fewer attempts available,<hex:02100103>the higher the payout!<hex:02100103><hex:02100103>Titan → 4 times<hex:02100103>Morbol → 5 times<hex:02100103>Cactuar → 6 times
column4: Swing the pickaxe to locate the<hex:02100103>hidden ore. The closer you are, the<hex:02100103>more the mining gauge is reduced.<hex:02100103>You win if the gauge reaches zero<hex:02100103>before you run out of attempts.

column3: Swing to determine<hex:02100103>the gauge speed.<hex:02100103>The higher the speed,<hex:02100103>the higher the payout!<hex:02100103><hex:02100103>Titan → Very fast<hex:02100103>Morbol → Fast<hex:02100103>Cactuar → Slow
column4: Swing the hatchet to locate the<hex:02100103>hidden timber. The closer you are,<hex:02100103>the more the gathering gauge is reduced.<hex:02100103>You win if the gauge reaches zero<hex:02100103>before you run out of attempts.
